title: Silent Hill: Homecoming playthrough — Part 1
description: This game is nothing like previous Silent Hills. They decided to focus on combat mostly, and they took stuff from the 2006 movie, which is just not the best idea. The game has some moments that are creepy, and it's not like the combat is horrible, it's actually kind of decent. The graphics aren't bad either, except for character faces (other than the main character). Overall this game is mediocre. The PC port is fucking horrible too, which really makes it annoying.
